        <item>
            <title>傳 Microsoft 正開發自家手提遊戲機　申請 Joy-Con 式手掣專利</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/xbox-handheld-console-rumor/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xbox-handheld-console-rumor</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/xbox-handheld-console-rumor/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 09:00:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[JoyCon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[xbox]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1218905</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>資深科技媒體人 Jez Corden 日前在 X （前稱 Twitter）爆料指 Xbox 內部批准多項新硬件開發計劃，消息指這批新硬件與 Xbox 自家掌上遊戲機有關。Jez Corden 更指「Microsoft 將無可避免要推出手提 Xbox」。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Why I believe more than EVER, an Xbox &quot;handheld&quot; is inevitably part of Microsoft&#39;s gaming future. </p><p>READ: <a href="https://t.co/cGeTvGAKMp">https://t.co/cGeTvGAKMp</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Xbox?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Xbox</a></p><p>&mdash; Jez (@JezCorden) <a href="https://twitter.com/JezCorden/status/1753473580686290950?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 2, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>Jez Corden 另外亦回應了 Tom Henderson 的一條帖文，表示繼 Sony 之後， Xbox 亦會推出自家掌上遊戲機。Jez Corden 是一個著名科技媒體編輯，雖然其沒有提供確實時間表，但其消息來源一直非常可靠。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">They are.</p><p>&mdash; Jez (@JezCorden) <a href="https://twitter.com/JezCorden/status/1753112588966375480?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 1, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>據外媒《Game Rant》報道，Microsoft 正在開發類似 Switch Joy-Con 的可拆卸式遊戲手掣，並已為其申請專利，似乎側面印證 Xbox 正在開發手提式遊戲機。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218908" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240206153953-694x346.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="346" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240206153953-694x346.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240206153953.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：Game Rant</p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9_T4iTcBT0I">YouTube</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://gamerant.com/xbox-handheld-console-rumor/">Game Rant</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/JezCorden/status/1753473580686290950">JezCorden@X</a>、<a href="https://www.windowscentral.com/gaming/xbox/an-xbox-handheld-isnt-just-likely-to-happen-for-microsoft-its-absolutely-necessary">Windows Central</a>、<a href="https://gamerant.com/microsoft-nintendo-switch-joy-con-style-xbox-controllers-patent/">Game Rant</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/microsoft-bethesda-indiana-jones-and-the-great-circle-ps5-release/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">傳 Microsoft 高層考慮，將多款 Xbox 獨佔遊戲開放予 PS5、Switch</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Microsoft 遊戲部門裁員 1,900 人　前 Activision Blizzard 員工和 Xbox 團隊受影響</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/app-store-4/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">串流遊戲平台可上架 App Store     Xbox Cloud Gaming、NVIDIA GeForce NOW 或受惠</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/xbox-handheld-console-rumor/game-channel/">傳 Microsoft 正開發自家手提遊戲機　申請 Joy-Con 式手掣專利</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
