        <item>
            <title>Fujifilm X100VI 外觀流出　新機疑剔除 D-Pad</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/fujifilm-x100vi-unveil-no-d-pad/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fujifilm-x100vi-unveil-no-d-pad</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/fujifilm-x100vi-unveil-no-d-pad/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 08:00:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apsc]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[fujifilm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm X100]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm X100V]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm X100VI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旁軸相機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1218887</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Fujifilm 早前已透露將於本月 20 日舉行 X Summit 發布會，而其旗下廣受歡迎的定焦數碼相機 X100V 自 2020 年推出以來已 4 年歷史，如無意外將會迎來更新。日前著名 Fujifilm 爆料網站「Fuji Rumors」就分享了 X100V 後繼機（暫稱 X100VI）的流出照，雖然相片上有厚重的「格仔」，但仍然可以看到流出照片與 X100V 的不同之處。</span></p><p>與現行款 X100V 相比，流出的 X100VI 之「DISP/BACK」按鈕旁邊多了一個標誌。除此之外，據爆料人 Patrick FujiRumors 表示，X100VI 將不設 D-Pad。如消息屬實，X100VI 用家操作將需更依賴觸控螢幕。</p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1218893" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/x100viwatermark1scal-694x575.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="575" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/x100viwatermark1scal-694x575.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/x100viwatermark1scal.jpg 1087w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">▲X100VI 諜照，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.fujirumors.com/leaked-first-pixelated-images-of-fujifilm-x100vi-unveil-no-d-pad/">Fuji Rumors</a></span></p><p>流出的 X100VI 諜照上明顯可見除型號位置打了厚格外，快門轉盤亦被遮蔽，可能代表該部分也會有大革新。</p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218894" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/x100viwm-694x369.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/x100viwm-694x369.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/x100viwm.jpg 1273w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.fujirumors.com/leaked-first-pixelated-images-of-fujifilm-x100vi-unveil-no-d-pad/">Fuji Rumors</a></span></p><p>據《Fuji Rumors》估計，Fujifilm X100VI 的售價將會比 X100V 高 200 美元。Fuji Rumors 引述消息來源指，X100VI 的售價將會是 1,599 美元（約港幣 1.2 萬元）。</p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DB633iB5agQ&amp;ab_channel=PatrickFujiRumors">Patrick FujiRumors@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://www.fujirumors.com/leaked-first-pixelated-images-of-fujifilm-x100vi-unveil-no-d-pad/">Fuji Rumors</a></span></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/fujifilm-instax-pal-3/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Fujifilm INSTAX Pal 迷你相機，的骰便攜 + 一按即印又得、連落電話再印又得</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/fujifilm-gfx100-ii-review/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】FUJIFILM GFX100 II 中幅無反數碼相機   1 億像素試相 + Reala Ace 新菲林模擬 + 試最新人工智能對焦</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/fujifilm-x100vi-unveil-no-d-pad/dc/">Fujifilm X100VI 外觀流出　新機疑剔除 D-Pad</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
